title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show AUG-15-2014 FRI
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show AUG-15-2014 FRI


Dennis Prager Radio Show



Prager 20140815  03 Open Lines

Prager H3: Per usual callers set the agenda.

       Issues raised include: 
        why is the Arab world full of so many lies about Israel;
        should the police be militarized;         
        why does Dennis own a foreign car.


Prager 20140815  02 Happiness Hour: Levels of Forgiveness

Prager H2: Dennis welcomes back Dr. Stephen Marmer, clinical professor
        of psychiatry at UCLA and psychiatrist in private practice in 
        Brentwood, CA. Dr. Marmer outlines three levels of forgiveness
        and how they relate to personal happiness. 

         A Best of Prager Hour. Originally broadcast August 26, 2011.


Prager 20140815  01 New Facts

Prager H1: New facts emerge in the Ferguson shooting incident.
      One new fact is that the incident was precipitated by a robbery.
      But circumstances of the actual shooting are as confusing as ever.
      Did the cop shoot an innocent teen for no good reason or 
        did the cop feel his life was in danger and had no choice?
